1. What this project is

Pawsonality is a lighthearted 15-question personality quiz that maps a
user's answers to one of six animal archetypes (Wolf, Cat, Dog, Eagle, Owl,
Dolphin), then shows a results page with live trivia about each animal
pulled from a third-party Animals API.

Tagline from the homepage: "15 questions · 2 minutes · zero science."

